Again - I see the pattern here.. - I dislike the fact that we have multiple methods with the same name doing similar stuff. Arguments can be made that signature verification is part of the validation of the AuthnRequest so I'm fine with how you moved that around but could we simple replace this with




        Suggested change











                    validateAuthnRequest(authnRequest, sp);



                    checkDestination(authnRequest);



                    checkAcs(authnRequest, sp);






? I see no reason keeping the second validateAuthnRequest now

